{"cards":[{"lines":[{"type":"title","text":"Conducting the lab"},{"type":"headline","text":"Identify variables"},{"type":"headline","text":"Design system to record data"},{"type":"headline","text":"Write down the series of steps"},{"type":"headline","text":"Consider precision and accuracy"}]},{"lines":[{"type":"title","text":"Precision versus accuracy"},{"type":"headline","text":"Left: Accurate shots"},{"type":"headline","text":"Right: Precise shots"}]}],"definitions":[],"secText":["  <b>Lesson:<\/b>  <b>    <br \/>  <\/b>1. Create a testable question and determine the equipment and technology needed when <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='1' data-subsection='0'>conducting an experiment<\/a>.<b><br \/><\/b>2. Identify the <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='0'>variables in the lab<\/a>, write a procedure, record data, and be mindful of accuracy and precision when conducting an experiment.<b><br \/><\/b>3. <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='1'>Determine ways to recycle<\/a> when designing an experiment.<b><br \/><\/b>4. <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='2'>Determine ways to be safe<\/a> during an experiment.<b><br \/><\/b>5. Define <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='3' data-subsection='0'>precision and accuracy<\/a>.<b><br \/><\/b>6. Compare <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='3' data-subsection='1'>precision versus accuracy<\/a>.<b><br \/><\/b>7. Determine <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='3' data-subsection='2'>methods to be more precise and accurate<\/a> in experiments. Determine if <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='4' data-subsection='0'>data gathered in an experiment is reasonable<\/a>.<b><br \/><\/b>8. <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='4' data-subsection='0'>Analyze the data<\/a> collected in an experiment.<b><br \/><\/b>9. <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='3' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='5' data-subsection='0'>Present the findings<\/a> from an experiment.","  <b>Homework:<\/b>  <span class=\"KBExternalLink\"><a href=\"assign.html#OHW 3.05\">OHW 3.05<\/a><\/span>","  <b>Quick Review:<\/b>  <a class='pjumpToVideo' href='javascript:void(0)' data-video='true' data-vref='sum_sci_lab_procedures'>Lab Procedures<\/a>, <a class='pjumpToVideo' href='javascript:void(0)' data-video='true' data-vref='sum_precision_accuracy'>Precision versus Accuracy<\/a>, <a class='pjumpToVideo' href='javascript:void(0)' data-video='true' data-vref='sum_lab_part_2'>Lab Data and Presentation<\/a>"],"objNames":["wb_conduct_lab","wb_precision_accuracy_concepts2"]}